data.description: PRICE JUST REDUCED!!  Sellers want to GIFT new Buyers with existing 2.75% LOW INTEREST RATE! Take Advantage of this Assumable Loan with Monthly Payment of $1,794.00 P&I, approx $414,000.00 outstanding Loan amount, fully amortized.    This gorgeous, spacious, single-story, newly built Family Home is YOUR Dream Home!!  Don't miss out!!    Picture this: 5 Spacious Bedrooms, 3 Large Bathrooms, & a Primary Suite with a large Walk-in Closet. Two separate vanity sinks, perfectly spaced in the huge bathroom, offer you that extra touch of luxury. Unwind in the separate shower & bathtub for ultimate relaxation & privacy.    Step into your spacious Kitchen, the heart of your family's gatherings, breakfasts, & entertaining moments. This open-concept floorplan connects seamlessly to the large family room & formal dining areas, making hosting a breeze. You'll love the grand Kitchen Island, perfect for barstools.  The Large walk-in Pantry, and abundance of Cabinets fit all your storage needs. Plus, we've got your back—all kitchen appliances are included! Your Laundry Room is extra roomy & can adapt to Electric or Gas appliances.    Custom Shutters adorn this beautiful home throughout. As you step outside, you'll be welcomed by California-drought-resistant landscaping in the front yard, while the side & backyard are fenced for ultimate privacy. Let your imagination run wild, as there's ample space to create your dream outdoor paradise—whether it's a Spa/Pool, BBQ area, Gazebo, or Patio – the possibilities are endless!    For auto enthusiasts or storage lovers, this property offers possible RV Access and a Large 2 Car Garage. This East-Side Lancaster House provides easy access to the Freeway, Schools & Shopping like Starbucks, Walmart, Target, Home Depot, CVS, Wallgreens, Food for Less Supermarket, Bank of America, etc.    Don't forget the little extras: recessed ceiling lights, central air conditioning & heating, environmentally friendly & energy-efficient appliances, and solar panels. Rainbird auto-sprinkler system, & Vivint Home Security Camera System. The flooring is a combination of durable tile, vinyl, & soft carpet.    You'll enjoy the stunning desert landscapes of the Antelope Valley and witness the breathtaking bloom of California poppies at the nearby Antelope Valley California Poppy Reserve. If you're a fan of aerospace and defense, the renowned Edwards Air Force Base is just around the corner.    Your dream home in Lancaster is calling.
